        {
            "title": "美銀建議投資者保持選擇性,而非在標普500創新高時追漲",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GtKneRkHTHKMYgJTDfJwvg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/asian_2_M_1440047814.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 美國銀行(Bank of America)敦促投資者不要追逐大盤漲勢,主張即使標普500重返歷史高位,也應採取更具選擇性的投資策略。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行的賣方指標(SSI)——一個追蹤華爾街策略師對平衡型基金中股票配置平均建議比例的反向指標——在4月份維持在55.6%,與3月份持平,當時股市重返歷史高位。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該讀數比年初水平低30點子,但較一年前高出1.1個百分點,當時在\"解放日\"之後該指標曾跌至54.5%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-403ceda9-3223-360e-9bc3-27117400fe8d-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該指標目前處於中性區域,但更接近觸發賣出信號而非買入信號——距離前者僅1.9個百分點,而距離後者則有4.4個百分點,美銀策略師指出。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"目前55.6%的水平遠低於先前市場高峰時期達到的水平(通常超過59%),意味著標普500在未來12個月的價格回報率為13%——這是我們標普500目標價五項輸入數據之一(也是最看漲的輸入數據),\"策略師表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">標普500在4月份上漲超過10%,這是自1928年以來第98百分位的月度回報,主要受停火希望和強於預期的企業盈利推動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然而,這波漲勢高度集中在指數頂部。超大型股領漲,等權重指數落後於市值加權基準指數5個百分點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"只有23%的股票跑贏標普500,這是我們自1986年以來數據歷史中第四低的月度讀數,\"策略師強調。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管盈利背景強勁,該團隊指出\"股票供需動態惡化\"以及\"仍未解決的伊朗衝突的滯後影響\"等因素可能會對估值造成壓力,主張應保持選擇性而非在新高時買入指數。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">買方情緒與SSI數據一致,基金經理配置今年有所下降,但未顯示出恐慌跡象。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E9%8A%80%E5%BB%BA%E8%AD%B0%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E8%80%85%E4%BF%9D%E6%8C%81%E9%81%B8%E6%93%87%E6%80%A7-%E8%80%8C%E9%9D%9E%E5%9C%A8%E6%A8%99%E6%99%AE500%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98%E6%99%82%E8%BF%BD%E6%BC%B2-130155442.html",
